4. Feedback equation: dot(N) = -H + gamma_0 * Q_mem / N^3
5. Slow manifold condition: Q_mem = N^{5/2} / gamma_0
6. Departure from exact fixed point due to memory accumulation (dot(Q_mem) = N_s * H):
   Taking time derivative of slow manifold: dot(Q_mem) = (5/2) * N^{3/2} * dot(N) / gamma_0
   Equating to N_s * N^{-1/2}: dot(N) = (2/5) * gamma_0 * N_s * N^{-2}
7. Final epsilon: epsilon = 0.5 * N^{-1/2} * (2/5 * gamma_0 * N_s * N^{-2}) = 0.2 * gamma_0 * N_s * H^5
8. Tensor-to-scalar ratio: r = 16 * epsilon = 3.2 * gamma_0 * N_s * H^5

